    <h1>Configuring currencies</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can work with different currencies in plentymarkets. This is useful if you sell your items in several different countries. This page describes the currency settings that relate to all of the stores in your plentymarkets system. In addition, further currency settings relate to individual stores. This page also teaches you how to insert template variables under <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/setting-up-clients/cms#web-design">CMS » Web design</a> so that your customers can switch from one currency to another.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
